channel.title: Wisescape RSPS [667] Join Now!
channel.description:
Hey Everyone!
WiseScape RSPS is 2 weeks old and is a great server to play. I decided to take a few pictures and post it on here to see how many new players we could get online
(Sorry about the pictures being so big :/)
Some details about the server!
All working skills Many working bosses such as god wars, nex, kalphite king, nomad, bork and many more Friendly Community Seasonal Events Vote Boxes Much More!
Forums: http://wisescape.net/mybb/ Download Link: http://www.mediafire.com/download/7d6j4i5wi4l64k7/WiseScape+V1.5.jar Please sign up on the forums and put Reality as your referrer :P thanks!
Some Pictures of the server!
Home @ Yanille [IMG]http://i62.tinypic.com/2ajntkg.jpg[/img] ::shops [IMG]http://i60.tinypic.com/wjhtfr.jpg[/img] Skilling Teleports [IMG]http://i59.tinypic.com/1zg9g2a.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i61.tinypic.com/nqbrjs.jpg[/img] Dungeoneering [IMG]http://i61.tinypic.com/21b2bo6.jpg[/img] God Wars [IMG]http://i60.tinypic.com/2dshb4k.png[/img] Kalphite King [IMG]http://i58.tinypic.com/n17ble.jpg[/img] Thanks for reading and hope you join the server!
